---
layout: base.njk
title: "Signal — Test Harness"
showDemoModal: true
---

<section class="signal-test">
  <h1 class="signal-test-title">Signal Test Harness</h1>
  <p class="signal-test-desc">Launch the modal in each sub-agent mode. Close and relaunch to switch modes — same mode continues the session.</p>

  <div class="signal-test-modes">

    <div class="signal-test-mode signal-test-mode--primary">
      <div class="signal-test-mode-header">
        <h2 class="signal-test-mode-name">Visitor</h2>
        <span class="signal-test-mode-type">chatType: signal-visitor</span>
        <span class="signal-test-mode-badge">Primary</span>
      </div>
      <p class="signal-test-mode-desc">signalId: erik-burns — fits the visitor against the owner profile. Persona selector, lead capture.</p>
      <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="window.signalOpen && window.signalOpen({ signalId: 'erik-burns' })">
        Launch Visitor
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="signal-test-mode">
      <div class="signal-test-mode-header">
        <h2 class="signal-test-mode-name">Onboard</h2>
        <span class="signal-test-mode-type">chatType: signal-onboard</span>
      </div>
      <p class="signal-test-mode-desc">No signalId — scores the visitor for Signal readiness. Marketing homepage experience.</p>
      <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="window.signalOpen && window.signalOpen()">
        Launch Onboard
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="signal-test-mode">
      <div class="signal-test-mode-header">
        <h2 class="signal-test-mode-name">Owner</h2>
        <span class="signal-test-mode-type">chatType: signal-owner</span>
      </div>
      <p class="signal-test-mode-desc">signalId: erik-burns, mode: owner — diagnostic interface for the Signal profile owner.</p>
      <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="window.signalOpen && window.signalOpen({ signalId: 'erik-burns', mode: 'owner' })">
        Launch Owner
      </button>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
